"The following nodes were discovered using the iSCSI initiator "
"<b>%(initiatorName)s</b> using the portal IP address <b>%(portalAddress)s</"
"b>.  Please select which nodes you wish to log into:"
msgstr ""
"Следећи чворови су откривени коришћењем iSCSI покретача "
"<b>%(initiatorName)s</b> и портал ИП адресе <b>%(portalAddress)s</b>. Молимо "
"изаберите на које чворове желите да се пријавите:"

#: pyanaconda/modules/payloads/payload/dnf/dnf_manager.py:675
msgid ""
"The following software marked for installation has errors.\n"
